{
  "texts": [
    "We could refine the LASOMO framework to develop variance-adjusted versions of the metric.",
    "It could also be valuable to explore ways to extend the Rank Graduation Accuracy (RGA) metrics used in the point predictions (Giudici & Raffinetti (2025)) in the context of a probabilistic forecasting setting.",
    "Such a probabilistic implementation of RGA could improve robustness, as it would be less affected by outliers.",
    "Despite the rising popularity of ensemble models, there is currently a lack of comprehensive evaluation metrics to assess the individual contributions of each model.",
    "Traditional standard practice involves setting up a leaderboard to independently evaluate the accuracy and effectiveness of individual prediction models based on appropriate scoring rules."
  ]
}